In the Forest of Greater Faydark I was born. Abandoned at a very young age, I have no recollection of my parents. I was found by Guard Orcslayer and taken to the Faydark Champion's guildhall, where I was then taught the ways of Tunare and The Great Rangers of Kelethin. In return for the kindness of the Elves of Kelethin, I now travel the lands of Norrath helping those in need. I remember a journey to the Commons where I met a young Cleric Lady named Ursi who was In need of some help. I spent the afternoon with her killing the Undead near the tunnel. It was during one of our many conversations of the afternoon she invited me to join her family "Exodus Fellowship". After many seasons of wandering the lands I finally took her up on her offer. I am now a Proud Ranger of "Exodus Fellowship".

May Tunare Guide your Travels
Daliddar McDillydally
Proud Ranger of Exodus Fellowship
